cs.SD, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.SY

The paper deals with deep generative models applied to symbolic music, which falls under the sub-category of cs.SD (Sound). The use of Variational Autoencoders (VAEs) and Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) for style and domain transfer puts the paper in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The addition of discriminators to improve the fidelity of the transformed music suggests the sub-category of cs.SI (Signal Processing). Finally, the overall topic of music genre transfer falls under the sub-category of cs.SY (Systems and Control).
